Our Civil Liability Insurance Programme

Our Civil Liability Insurance Programme can provide compensation under a claim of financial loss made against Extrede LLC as a result of error, omission, negligence, fraud, or failure to perform our activities or services for a value of up to 5 million. The programme is underwritten by Lloyds of London, Read more.

Extrede LLC is a financial brokerage company regulated by Financial Conduct Authority (registration no. SE0389),
Cyprus Securities and Exchange Commission (licence no.182/015), the Central Bank of Curaao and Sint Maarten (license no. 0002ION).
and the Financial Services Commission (license no. SIBA/M/12/10344).

Extrede LLC. is registered United Kingdom with registration number 07593201 . 89 Gresham Street, 8th Floor, London EC2V 7JE, United Kingdom.

Risk Warning: There is a high level of risk involved when trading leveraged products such as CFDs. 79.43% of retail investor accounts lose money when trading CFDs with this provider. You should not risk more than you can afford to lose, you may lose the entire amount of your account balance. You should not trade or invest unless you fully understand the true extent of your exposure to the risk of loss. When trading or investing, you must always take into consideration the level of your experience. Copy-trading services imply additional risks to your investment due to the nature of such products. If the risks involved seem unclear to you, please apply to an outside specialist for independent advice.

Extrede LLC and its affiliates do not target EU/EEA clients. The marketing material on this website is not intended for UK residents.
